    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1876-06-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1876-06-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="156" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d156">
                <head>No. 146.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1876-06-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 17,
                                1876</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Fish</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Winslow discharged by Judge Mellor in chambers. Judge Lindley refused to
                            act on Brent’s application; referred it to court <hi rend="italic">in
                                banco</hi> on Monday.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>HOFFMAN.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
